properties.name: Greentree Vintage Circle Grove Garden of the Giant Azaleas
properties.description: The Vintage Circle Grove Garden of Giant Azaleas is a very old spot where Azaleas grow so high you can walk inside like a mini forest. These evergreens burst with magenta or purple flowers in the summer. Great for photos!

properties.name: Vinatge Greentree Glacial Bolders Gongshi Decor Park
properties.description: Giant Glacial Bolders left behind by Prehistoric Glaciers in the Ice Age too massive to move were incorporated as Chinese Gongshi Art Decor. This Park Still has the original bolders, new benches, lampposts, and lots of shade in the summer.

properties.name: The Fairy Tree Grove

properties.name: The Marshy Ruins of the Vintage Greentree Baseball Park
properties.description: The actual remnants and ruins of the old bases from the Baseball park are still in the ground. It used to be a Baseball field, but is overrun by marshy soil over the years. Greentree still gives newsletters telling residents about the baseball field.

properties.name: South Field Engtrance Sakura Grove 02
